Title: Halloweentown II: Kalabar's Revenge
Writer: Jon Cooksey, Ali Marie Matheson, Paul Bernbaum (based on characters created by)
Actors: Kimberly J. Brown, Judith Hoag, Daniel Kountz, Joey Zimmerman
Plot: The Cromwell clan split their time between the real world and "Halloweentown", but the son of an old rival threatens to make the latter "real" and the real world a place of monsters.
